openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Examples
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /:
    get:
      operationId: getRoot
      parameters:
        - name: Content-Type
          in: header
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
          example: application/json
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
        '400':
          description: 'Invalid value for: header Content-Type: application/json'
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
